|                Commands                |
|  Object Movements :                    |
|     - ↑ : Move Forward                 |
|     - ↓ : Move Backward                |
|     - → : Move Right                   |
|     - ← : Move Left                    |
|     - PgUp : Move Up                   |
|     - PgDown : Move Down               |
|     - LEFT_SHIFT : x2 speed            |
|                                        |
|   Camera Movements :                   |
|     - W : Move Forward                 |
|     - A : Move Backward                |
|     - S : Move Right                   |
|     - D : Move Left                    |
|     - Space : Move Up                  |
|     - Left_Ctrl : Move Down            |
|     - LEFT_SHIFT : x2 speed            |
|     - Right_Click Mouse : Rotate       |
|                                        |
|   Tools :                              |
|     - R : Reset Object                 |
|     - C : Reset Camera                 |
|     - P : Stop auto-rotation           |
|     - TAB : Open Gui                   |
